title: Maybe Today Satan Funny Men/Unisex T-Shirt
excerpt:
Everybody has their day
Say hello to your new favorite t-shirt. Our tees feature a classic set-in crew neck collar, a modern fit with tapered shoulders make it an ideal choice for a wide range of body types. Side seam stitched construction ensures it keeps its shape wash after wash. We use an incredibly soft cotton thatâ€™s combed and ringspun. With a fabric weight of 4.2 oz, they have just the right amount of comfort and breathability.
Solid colors feature 100% cotton, heather colors feature a 52/48 cotton/poly blend with the exception of Athletic Heather which is a 90/10 blend. Fabric is not pre-shrunk so some shrinking should be expected.
